side of things. We've used several different types of machine learning models, and we test

00:18:10.219 --> 00:18:15.020
different ones to see which ones are the most accurate. We are specifically focusing in this

00:18:15.020 --> 00:18:21.739
type of case on classification models, where we are trying to predict a binary outcome of did the

00:18:21.739 --> 00:18:27.180
employee stay or did they leave based on all of the historical data that we've gathered of employees

